### 1) 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8081/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "yang",
  "email": "yang123@example.com",
  "password": "yang123"
}


### 2) 로그인
POST http://localhost:8081/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "kim",
  "password": "kim123"
}

### 3) 로그아웃
POST http://localhost:8081/users/kim/logout
X-USER-ID: 1


### 4). 회원 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8081/users/kim
X-USER-ID: 1


### 5-1) 이메일 변경
PUT http://localhost:8081/users/kim
Content-Type: application/json
X-USER-ID: 1

{
  "email": "kim123@example.com"
}


###  5-2) 비밀번호 변경
PUT http://localhost:8081/users/kim/password
Content-Type: application/json
X-USER-ID: 1

{
  "currentPassword": "kim123",
  "newPassword": "kim1234",
  "confirmPassword": "kim1234"
}


