### 6) 멤버 키워드 검색 (username/email LIKE)
GET http://localhost:8081/users?query=im


### 7) 멤버 일괄 검색
GET http://localhost:8081/users/batch?ids=1,2,3


### 8) 회원 탈퇴 (Soft Delete, 보호 엔드포인트)
DELETE http://localhost:8081/users/choi
X-USER-ID: 7


